		  <td class="forum_boardrow1" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 1px;" valign="top"><div id="message30182001">Code Geass is one of those shows that you just turn off your brain and just watch. To think about it any more than needed is to do yourself a great disservice. Yeah there are plot holes, yeah there are inconsistencies in character development, yeah the show's logic is just plain stupid, but if you can bring yourself to just not care about it, the show is just a pure adrenaline thrill ride.</div><div class="postActions"></div></td>
