		  </td>
		  <td class="forum_boardrow1" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 1px;" valign="top"><div id="message30207185"><!--quote--><div class="quotetext"><strong>Miraclezify said:</strong><!--quotesaid--><br>Code Geass is one of those shows that you just turn off your brain and just watch. To think about it any more than needed is to do yourself a great disservice. Yeah there are plot holes, yeah there are inconsistencies in character development, yeah the show's logic is just plain stupid, but if you can bring yourself to just not care about it, the show is just a pure adrenaline thrill ride.<!--quote--></div><br />
I agree with this. The show is retarded as hell but I did have fun with it, I just can't consider it <em>good</em> because it takes itself seriously.</div><div class="postActions"></div><div class="sig"><!--link--><a href="http://myanimelist.net/clubs.php?cid=35120"><img class="userimg" data-src="http://i.imgur.com/MkmghXm.jpg" /></a></div></td>
		</tr></table></div><div class="forum_boardrowspacer">&nbsp;</div>
